     --data-binary {}

&quot;application/octet-stream&quot; is a generic binary data type, meaning it can be used to represent any type of binary data. This MIME type is commonly used when the content type of the data is unknown or when the data being transferred does not fit any other specific MIME type. It is often used to transfer files or raw binary data.

